---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="bg-white border-t border-[var(--color-rule)] mt-24">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between gap-8">
      <div>
        <p class="text-[var(--color-ink)] font-medium text-base mb-2">Plant Life Navi</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-ink-sub)] leading-relaxed">植物とともに、豊かな暮らしを。</p>
        <a href="https://x.com/plant_navi_jp" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mt-4 text-sm text-[var(--color-ink-mute)] hover:text-[var(--color-ink)] transition-colors">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M18.244 2.25h3.308l-7.227 8.26 8.502 11.24H16.17l-5.214-6.817L4.99 21.75H1.68l7.73-8.835L1.254 2.25H8.08l4.713 6.231zm-1.161 17.52h1.833L7.084 4.126H5.117z"/></svg>
          @plant_navi_jp
        </a>
      </div>
      <nav class="flex flex-col gap-2.5 text-sm">
        <a href="/houseplant/" class="text-[var(--color-ink-sub)] hover:text-[var(--color-ink)] transition-colors">観葉植物</a>
        <a href="/succulent/" class="text-[var(--color-ink-sub)] hover:text-[var(--color-ink)] transition-colors">多肉植物</a>
        <a href="/gardening/" class="text-[var(--color-ink-sub)] hover:text-[var(--color-ink)] transition-colors">ガーデニング</a>
        <a href="/about/" class="text-[var(--color-ink-sub)] hover:text-[var(--color-ink)] transition-colors">運営者情報</a>
        <a href="/privacy-policy/" class="text-[var(--color-ink-sub)] hover:text-[var(--color-ink)] transition-colors">プライバシーポリシー</a>
        <a href="/profile/" class="text-[var(--color-ink-sub)] hover:text-[var(--color-ink)] transition-colors">プロフィール</a>
        <a href="/disclaimer/" class="text-[var(--color-ink-sub)] hover:text-[var(--color-ink)] transition-colors">免責事項</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
    <div class="border-t border-[var(--color-rule)] mt-10 pt-6 text-xs text-[var(--color-ink-mute)] text-center space-y-1">
      <p>当サイトはアフィリエイト広告を掲載しています。</p>
      <p>&copy; {year} Plant Life Navi. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
